extendedInfo.description: This is a special editon of FRANK's ADVENTURES - LETTES for Kids.Hello! My name is Frank. I used to be an ordinary farmer. I lived in a small village where every day was the same.I worked the plantations and took care of the animals.Until one night, everything changed.I never thought that night my life will change completely.It all started in the cosmos....I got up out of bed and then I saw my outfit.It was not a dream! I really could fly. I had a great drive boots and overalls for flying between the stars.And then I reminded myself everything.I reminded myself that I am no longer an ordinary Frank, I'm a superhero. I am a man who has super strength and super skills.I'm a Jet-Man!Thus began my adventure in the sky.You can join it. Just come to my game.JET-MAN FRANEK starts a long journey by:* Family lowlands, - A-I* Mexican steppes,- J-R - full version only* Passes Collorado, - S-Z - full version only* Egyptian darkness, - a-i - full version only* Inuit polar nights, - j-r - full version only* Dutch depression, - s - z - full version only* Australian beaches - 1-9 - full version onlyand finally  the big city... 10-18 - full version onlyHelp Frank. It is recommended to install the DEMO version before purchasing the full version to verify compatibility with your device.Visit Frank at his home page http://dazz.com.pl Like Frank's fanpage http://facebook.com/dazzstudio;Learn how to control the Frank's engines http://dazz.com.pl/jet-man-i-tylko-dwa-przyciski-pomocy/.Software JET-MAN LETTERS DEMO is a demo version - does not include all levels and functions.Search for the full version at play.google.
